 Bella Shmurda has taken to Twitter to reflect on becoming successful in the Nigerian music industry. The star made it known that he now has 550 million streams on all platforms stating he would have still been at Lagos state university where he was an undergraduate student, wining and dining with carryovers and stranded with nothing in his pocket. READ ALSO: I Don’t Accept Apology; I Believe In Revenge – Bella Shmurda Bella revealed that he is thankful to God for everything and how far he has come. Although he did not say much, but he is proud of himself and he is happy where he is now. 